The paper discusses the integration of human strategies into deep reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of deep learning methods is also mentioned, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the development of a multi-agent environment, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the cooperative learning of multiple agents, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
